Package: filibustr
Title: Data Utilities for Congressional Research
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: person("Max", "Feinleib", email = "mhfeinleib@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID =
        "0009-0002-9604-3533"))
Description: Provides easy-to-understand and consistent interfaces for
        accessing data on the U.S. Congress. The functions in
        'filibustr' streamline the process for importing data on
        Congress into R, removing the need to download and work from
        CSV files and the like. Data sources include 'Voteview'
        (<https://voteview.com/>), the U.S. Senate website
        (<https://www.senate.gov/>), and more.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://feinleib.github.io/filibustr/,
        https://github.com/feinleib/filibustr
